metadata.description:
SPINNING I AM SO SPUN OUT
 
A LIFETIME OF
ROMANTIC OBSESSION
AND FEMALE FANTASY
COMPRESSED INTO
A HYPERSENSORY LANDSCAPE
 
"SPIN MY HEART AROUND AND
AROUND FLYING AND I CAN'T
COME DOWN I'M HIGH AS HELL
AND I CAN'T LET GO OH
CAROUSEL"
